<br>
There are 25 languages - 23 should be at your trainer depending on your level...<br>
<br>
With the latest patch, you do NOT need to zone nor do you have to have someone teach you (if it's a bug or what, I don't know...) - All you need is 2 people, and 1 pt in any language skill - in 10 minutes, you can have it mastered....<br>
<br>
All you do is sit in group with someone - spam them with one character ...  As you do, they'll learn and you'll get skill ups by practicing...  When they get a skill up, they should spam you...  This will further speed up learning languages (you get a language check every time you say something - and every time they say something to you...)<br>
